            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>At Amani Skin Care, we value your privacy and want you to feel confident when using our platform. This Privacy Policy outlines how we gather, use, and safeguard your personal information when you visit our website to book your personalized skincare sessions.</p>

            <h2>What Information Do We Collect?</h2>
            <p>When you interact with our website, register for our services, or book an appointment, we collect the following types of information to enhance your experience:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> This includes details such as your name, email address, phone number, and any other necessary information to complete your appointment booking.</li>
                <li><strong>Skin Care Preferences:</strong> Information about your skin concerns and treatment preferences, ensuring that we can recommend and provide tailored services for your unique needs.</li>
                <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> We process your payment securely through trusted payment services. Rest assured, we do not store any of your sensitive payment details.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>How Do We Use Your Information?</h2>
            <p>Your information helps us deliver a smooth and personalized service to you. Here's how we utilize the data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To confirm and manage your appointments and bookings efficiently.</li>
                <li>To provide personalized skincare treatments based on your unique preferences and needs.</li>
                <li>To send timely reminders and updates about your upcoming sessions, ensuring you never miss an appointment.</li>
                <li>To enhance our services and user experience by analyzing how you use our platform.</li>
                <li>To stay in touch and provide you with relevant updates, including special offers and skincare tips.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Your Privacy Rights</h2>
            <p>We respect your rights when it comes to your personal data. You have the following rights:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Access:</strong> You can view the personal information we hold about you.</li>
                <li><strong>Update:</strong> Feel free to update or correct your details whenever necessary.</li>
                <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Request to delete your personal data, subject to legal considerations.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>How We Protect Your Information</h2>
            <p>Your trust is important to us, and we take all necessary precautions to protect your data. We use encryption, secure servers, and the latest technology to ensure that your personal information is safe from unauthorized access.</p>

            <h2>Changes to Our Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally to reflect changes in our practices or to comply with legal requirements. Any updates will be posted on this page, so we encourage you to check back regularly to stay informed.</p>

